         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#chaniotis2016a">
            <p> The people buried Theodotos, son of Hermias, the priest of Hestia Boulaia, a good and virtuous man, a lover of the fatherland 
               continuing the tradition of his ancestors, who lived a good and prudent life, 
               in love of learning, in education, and in the entire virtue.</p>
         </div>
